{"tid":641323,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係我身上睇唔到未來","createTime":"2018-04-25T02:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T04:29:04.000Z","uid":117365,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e53f4279ee0bc444934dde40f3f2ebfd16470a","tid":641323,"uid":117365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:26:41.000Z","msg":"純發洩 歡迎評論<br />\n<br />\n前幾日比前任飛左<br />\n（利申：分左第二次手 之前分開左一個禮拜因爲我好唔捨得，做左死狗氹返佢，點知比我發現佢係酒吧識左第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但最後我都追返佢）<br />\n<br />\n正題：<br />\n分手原因話我少少野都發脾氣<br />\n話係我身上睇唔到未來<br />\n又話唔係睇唔到 但有98%既未來都唔想同我一齊<br />\n<br />\n講真：我又衰既 我因為擔心佢會肚餓 叫佢食多啲<br />\n佢唔食我又發脾氣，佢同男仔玩得開心我又發脾氣，我返工有壓力又發脾氣，係佢心目中佢做咩我都淨係識發脾氣。<br />\n<br />\n但我每次發脾氣佢有99%都唔會主動氹我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （就算佢知自己錯都要講到我錯）<br />\n<br />\n利申：我自問自己都幾上進 為左前途同佢既將來，就算攰_到pk都繼續返工，佢一句要我草假請佢旅行，我假都唔敢放。<br />\n<br />\n樓主真係好想知「係我身上睇唔到將來」係點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3924026186655db4dc023f63f1635554dd339739","tid":641323,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:34:33.000Z","msg":"冷靜D照下鏡,睇下自己個樣, 同埋睇下你本銀行存摺有幾多錢先啦   世界好公平   如果人人都心想事成  會天下大亂  世上總要有你D咁既廢人"},{"pid":"98d6f679ff0